5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

pointer-sheet

Generic function

Summary

Returns the sheet under the specified pointer.

Signature

pointer-sheet pointer => sheet

Arguments

pointer
An instance of type <pointer>.

Values

sheet
An instance of type false-or(<sheet>).

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description

Returns the sheet under pointer, or #f if there is no sheet under the pointer.

See also

pointer-position, page 328

Functional Developer Library Reference: DUIM - 3 Dec 1998
